com.soebes.maven.plugins.doxygen

Class DoxygenReportTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.soebes.maven.plugins.doxygen.TestBase
      • com.soebes.maven.plugins.doxygen.TestDoxygenBase
        • com.soebes.maven.plugins.doxygen.DoxygenReportTest

  • public class DoxygenReportTest
extends TestDoxygenBase
    These are the Unit test which check if a value will be written to the configuration file. In every test case the file with a value for a particular configuration item is created than the file is read and the item is compared with the stored value. Afterwards the created file is removed.
    Author:
    Karl Heinz Marbaise
